OL,7,FMore than 80,000 people visited a
OL,8,Fcommunity warm space last week, as
OL,9,Fplummeting temperatures forced
OL,10,Fstruggling bill-payers to seek shelter
OL,11,Foutside their own homes amid the cost
OL,12,Fof living crisis.
OL,14,FThe Warm Welcome campaign is a network
OL,15,Fof around 3,000 organisations across
OL,16,Fthe UK, ranging from churches to local
OL,17,Fauthorities, which have opened their
OL,18,Fdoors to offer respite from the cold
OL,19,Fthis winter, often providing food and
OL,20,Fdrink.
OL,3,CSurge in Britons using warmbanks as
OL,4,CArctic blast leaves people struggling
OL,5,Cto heat their homes
